description:
You guys, when I tell you it took 19 years to get this to download correctly and then at the end of everything the theme song refused to play...GarageBand sucks! Anyway, hello! Caroline and Jackie here to talk about our favorite must-travel-with items! And we're also here to sing for you, which I know you guys love and we don't wanna withhold our talent from you.


Shop the Gee Thanks shelf for all recs!: https://shoplist.us/geethanksjustboughtit


Here's what we discuss:

  • Wander Airplane Mode Travel Set: https://fave.co/3eErSqV
  • Foot Hammock: https://amzn.to/33AyPmH
